      <title>Hexo(1)-Hello Hexo</title>
      <link href="/2020/02/28/Tech-hexo-1/"/>
      <url>/2020/02/28/Tech-hexo-1/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div align="center">    <img src="/2020/02/28/Tech-hexo-1/hexo.png" width="80%"></div><h2 id="关于搭建博客"><a href="#关于搭建博客" class="headerlink" title="关于搭建博客"></a>关于搭建博客</h2><p>事情的起由是大概一年前买了个域名，然后正好把它解析到我买的服务器上，搭建了一个基于<a href="https://wordpress.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WordPress</a>的动态博客，主要是在LAMP上做的。当时也就搭着玩的没想写东西，然而在某个重要的时间点后，服务器IP被墙了…</p><p>之后就考虑搭一个静态的不被墙的博客，主要看了<a href="https://jekyllrb.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Jekyll</a>和<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hexo</a>，前者是用Ruby的而且Github支持比较好，后者用的Node.js而且用户也很多。但是我看中了Hexo快速、简洁且高效的特性(实际上是看上某些<a href="https://hexo.io/themes/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">themes</a>了…)，所以索性上船了，配合Github Page还是很方便的。</p><p>主题用的是<a href="http://blackshow.me/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Freemind.386</a>，喜欢这种风格的界面。其实我更想做成类似<a href="http://kristopolous.github.io/BOOTSTRA.386/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">BOOTSTRA.386</a>，可是我是前端菜鸡，上一次用还是5年以前简单的HTML+CSS，甚至没用过JavaScript。哪天等我变强了，我再改改吧。<br></p><div>    <img src="/2020/02/28/Tech-hexo-1/TBC.png" width="30%"></div><h2 id="Hexo-Quick-Start"><a href="#Hexo-Quick-Start" class="headerlink" title="Hexo Quick Start"></a>Hexo Quick Start</h2><h3 id="Create-a-new-post"><a href="#Create-a-new-post" class="headerlink" title="Create a new post"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">"My New Post"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Writing</a></p><h3 id="Run-server"><a href="#Run-server" class="headerlink" title="Run server"></a>Run server</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/server.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Server</a></p><h3 id="Generate-static-files"><a href="#Generate-static-files" class="headerlink" title="Generate static files"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">// or</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Generating</a></p><h3 id="Deploy-to-remote-sites"><a href="#Deploy-to-remote-sites" class="headerlink" title="Deploy to remote sites"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo deploy</span><br><span class="line">// or</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Deployment</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
